<BlogPageParagraph>
    The <Anchor To="docs/extensions/datagrid/getting-started" Title="Link to DataGrid component">DataGrid component</Anchor> is powerful and flexible, allowing developers to display and manipulate tabular data. It supports advanced features such as sorting, filtering, paging, and virtual scrolling, which makes it easy to handle large datasets.
