<BlogPageParagraph>
    The <Anchor To="docs/components/date-picker" Title="Link to DatePicker component">DatePicker component</Anchor> is another valuable UI component that allows users to select a date from a calendar control. It supports different date formats and localization, which makes it easy to handle other date formats across different cultures.
